            "title": "港股開跌228點   科網金礦股跌   摯達科技首掛飆1.9倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數開跌228點或0.85%，報26523點，恒生國企開跌89點或 0.94%，報9440點 ; 恒生科技指數跌90點或1.4%，報6380點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交35.58億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)跌2.42%，報169.1元; 騰訊(00700)跌0.96%，報669點，成交居首二位。百度(09888)跌2.25%，報130.5元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今日首掛摯達科技(02650)較招股飆183.92%，報190元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金股齊挫。萬國黃金(03929)挫2.42%，報39,5元; 紫金(02899)跌1.16%，報35.72元; 紫金黃金國際(02259)挫3.75%，報136元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中興通訊(00763)升3.41%，報41.82元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)跌0.39%，報103.6元; 恒生(00011)報149.8元，無升跌。</p>\n</div>",
